snippet.title: Sonic Moon BETA stuff {05/12/2021}
snippet.description:
I was considering doing a full playthrough but then I though "Nah, I'll just show you the main things I want to focus on."
* Sailor Mars gameplay.
* Recomposed a bit of Contrast Coast Z's music.
* New Special Stage music.
* More of Ruby Ruins Zone.
* Soundwave Star Zone's new tile animations.
* Super and Hyper Sonic.
* Final Boss tweaks.
* Final game tally.

Game Jolt Page: https://gamejolt.com/games/sonicthehedgehogmoon/568526

Sonic is owned by SEGA / Sonic Team.
Sailor Moon is owned by Naoko Takeuchi / Toei.
This project is fan-made and non-profit.

Mario Obsessed - MMXXI
20 days 'till Christmas Day!
